header.masthead
    div.container.h-100
      div.row.h-100.align-items-center.justify-content-center.text-center
        div.col-lg-10.align-self-end
          h1.text-uppercase.text-white.font-weight-bold This is Vocabulary-app for english learners!
          hr.divider.my-4
        div.col-lg-8.align-self-baseline
          p.text-white-75.font-weight-light.mb-5 自分で例文を作って単語帳に登録したり、画像を紐づけて単語帳に登録することは、記憶力向上に役立ちます！
          = link_to 'ログインして使ってみる', words_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-xl'
          a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.js-scroll-trigger href="#about" Find Out More

section.page-section.bg-primary#about
    div.container
      div.row.justify-content-center
        div.col-lg-8.text-center
